properties.media:imagetext:
YOUR WINTER VACATION
IN MEXICO
BEGINS WHEN YOU BOARD A FLAGSHIP
10 MATTER HOW SHORT a vacation you have, your
Mexican siesta is only hours away by smooth, fast
American Airlines' Flagships. Controlled pressure,
air-conditioning, radiant heating, club-like reclining
chairs — these all contribute to make your Flagship
flight a memorybook experience.
Only American offers daily direct DC-6 service to Mexico
City — the Aztec from New York and the East, the Toltec from
Chicago and the Mid-West, the Mayan from Los Angeles and
the West.
And Flagship travel costs you less than you think! Delicious,
full-course meals are served with American's compliments.
There is no tipping — no extras to bother with. Your fare cost
is the complete cost — and a 10% saving on your return flight
when you buy a round-trip ticket. Then, there's the famous
American Family Fare Plan which has been extended to include
travel all the way to Mexico City. That means you can take the
family with you for ½ the fare on certain days of the week.
This is the year to exchange winter for Mexico's June-like
climate. Exchange rates are low — more for your American
dollar than ever before. Ultra-modern hotels, sophisticated night
life and colorful sightseeing in a magic land of contrasts will
make this vacation the most exciting of your life.
This winter — meet MEXICO!

Travel Agent or any American Airlines Office
